  "detailed_description": "Welcome to <i>Land of Dread!</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1016350/extras/ac056fbad095cac8073956521f314cad.poster.avif?t=1594928704\" width=244 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1016350/extras/ac056fbad095cac8073956521f314cad.webm?t=1594928704\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1016350/extras/16dd3d39bdf613b93851fe724f53ac6b.webp?t=1594928704\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1016350/extras/16dd3d39bdf613b93851fe724f53ac6b.poster.avif?t=1594928704\" class=\"bb_img\" width=169 height=210 /></picture></span><br><br><i>Land of Dread</i> is an isometric colony simulator with an emphasis on gathering resources, building resource-generating structures, and fighting hostile demons. Upgrade existing structures, assign jobs to colonists, and invest gold into resource imports.<br><br><strong>100% indie, Land of Dread features custom sprites and an immersive, eerie soundtrack composed by Kevin MacLeod.</strong><br><br><strong>Gather:</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1016350/extras/0250ac313450f0da82266a6fd9b76cd5.webp?t=1594928704\" width=37 height=39 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1016350/extras/2ffd5291c1b1884038edb7596bfb0b81.webp?t=1594928704\" width=46 height=45 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1016350/extras/51640699eb6500d2497125388d9aa6e0.webp?t=1594928704\" width=44 height=39 /></span><br><br><i>Food:</i> The bread and butter of the colony.<br><i>Gold:</i> Used to permanently increase daily resource income through a banking structure at the price of 50g/1 resource per day. Also affects score.<br><i>Stone:</i> Used to upgrade buildings.<br><i>Wood:</i> Required for all buildings.<br><br>Resources respawn every 6 hours, but can also be earned each hour/day by constructing specific buildings and/or upgrading the bank.<br><br><strong>Build:</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1016350/extras/9661f428c983d86d47bb2bfc0945cb12.avif?t=1594928704\" width=215 height=217 /></span><br><br><i>Hut:</i> +1 Gold/Hour.<br><i>Bank:</i> +50 Gold/Day. Allows purchase of resources.<br><i>Shop:</i> +3 Food/Day.<br><i>Home:</i> +1 Colonists/Day.<br><i>Mine:</i> +1 Stone/Hour.<br><br>All buildings can be upgraded indefinitely for a flat fee of 100 stone per upgrade.<br><br><strong>Colonists:</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1016350/extras/2976b286c913be6dd8c73b5381a9f047.webp?t=1594928704\" width=58 height=147 /></span><br><br><i>Farmer:</i> +1 Food/Hour.<br><i>Logger:</i> +1 Wood/Hour.<br><i>Miner:</i> +1 Stone/Hour.<br><br>All colonists can be assigned jobs of your choosing and provide daily tax income.<br><br><strong>Sell:</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1016350/extras/bb70cf47f0b52b0893504375915f999d.webp?t=1594928704\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1016350/extras/bb70cf47f0b52b0893504375915f999d.poster.avif?t=1594928704\" class=\"bb_img\" width=20 height=35 /></picture></span><br><i>Food:</i> 1 Food for 1 Gold.<br><i>Stone:</i> 1 Stone for 2 Gold.<br><i>Wood:</i> 1 Wood for 3 Gold.<br><br>Excess resources can be sold at any time.<br><br><strong>Tutorial:</strong><br><br><strong>An in-game tutorial is available at any time. Simply left-click on the player to display the tutorial.</strong>",
